data.description: Spectacular move in ready 4 bedroom/3 full bath 3164 square foot home in beautiful Mallory Creek Plantation! Seller will  pay $10,000 towards closing costs with acceptable offer. Enjoy the amenities at the competition size pool, Gather with family and friends at the low country Clubhouse1 Enjoy the many walking paths and playgrounds. Fabulous kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and a breakfast nook! Wood  and tile flooring throughout the home! Large living room and a dining room. Spectacular master bedroom with trey ceiling, walk in closets, tiled shower, and  soaking tub,. 3 other bedrooms and a spacious Bonus room! Nicely manicured landscaping on a large lot. Screened in porch with  a large back yard with fencing that backs up to the woods. Just minutes from  Downtown Wilmington. Enjoy  the many near by Beaches ! Come take a look!
